Do as the script says...

Then hit "Save As" title it whateveryouwant.mrc, load it, and save and exit.

Test it out in somewhere where no one will be offended, and once you have it fine tuned feel free to use it only when necessary and stop if asked to in a channel (it's a fun script to compare progress on new popular torrents, but not if you overdo it).

Just type /uthelp to see all the commands.

